&lt;li&gt;Travel to customer sites to observe how people actually use our products in the field, and bring that context back into every design decision you make&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Take on the Sage dashboard, our AI-driven insights layer, as your second product surface, shaping a product that’s still early enough that your decisions will define its direction&lt;/li&gt;
